  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Admin Executive",
  "description": "<p>Veertech Pte. Ltd. is seeking a Sales Admin Executive to support our sales and business development team with day-to-day administrative and coordination duties. This role is ideal for someone who is organised, detail-oriented, and comfortable working in a fast-paced environment.</p><p>Key Responsibilities</p><p>Provide administrative support to the sales and business development team</p><p>Prepare quotations, invoices, delivery orders, and sales documentation</p><p>Coordinate with clients, suppliers, and internal teams on orders and timelines</p><p>Maintain accurate sales records, databases, and filing systems</p><p>Follow up on customer enquiries and support sales activities</p><p>Assist with tender submissions and contract documentation where required</p><p>Handle general office and ad-hoc administrative duties</p><p>Requirements</p><p>Diploma or equivalent qualification</p><p>Minimum 1–2 years of experience in sales administration or related role</p><p>Proficient in Microsoft Office (Excel, Word, Outlook)</p><p>Good organisational and communication skills</p><p>Able to work independently and as part of a team</p><p>Attention to detail and good follow-through</p><p>Experience in engineering, marine, offshore, or industrial sectors is an advantage</p><p><br />What We Offer</p><p>Competitive salary commensurate with experience</p><p>Stable working environment</p><p>Opportunity to work with an experienced sales and operations team</p><p>Exposure to marine, offshore, and industrial projects</p>",
